---
import CustomImage from '@/components/CustomImage'
import ImageCarousel from '@/components/ImageCarousel'
import CardCarousel from '@/components/CardCarousel'
import StickyHeader from '@/components/StickyHeader'
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout'

const SITE_TITLE = 'Echolodia'
---

<BaseLayout title={SITE_TITLE}>
	<StickyHeader
		title='Echolodia'
		buyUrl='https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2992734276'
		buyLabel='Subscribe on the Workshop'
		exploreLabel='Tech Specs'
		exploreUrl='#specs'
	/>
	<div>
		<h1 class='title text-6xl font-bold'>{SITE_TITLE}</h1>
		<h2 class='text-3xl font-medium mt-4 mb-10'>Dream Machine</h2>
		<CustomImage
			imagePath='/src/assets/images/stormworks/echolodia/hero.jpg'
			altText='Dream Machine'
		/>
		<div class='flex justify-center mt-10'>
			<div
				class='w-fit px-4 py-1.5 text-sm rounded-full bg-sky-500 hover:bg-sky-600 text-white font-medium transition-colors'
			>
				<a href='https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2992734276' target='_blank'
					>Subscribe on the Workshop</a
				>
			</div>
		</div>

		<article class='prose prose-xl dark:prose-invert w-full max-w-none mt-8'>
			<h2>Design</h2>
			<p>
				The Echolodia is our longest lasting vehicle lineup ever, with this being the 5th generation
				truck. While the core philosophies have stayed the same, this truck has proved to test the
				limits of what's possible, and has quickly become one of the most capable, and best land
				vehicles in Stormworks. This year, we've added many, many quality of life features to make
				using the Echolodia easier than ever.
			</p>
			<CustomImage
				imagePath='/src/assets/images/stormworks/echolodia/rear.jpg'
				altText='The Echolodia 2023, the latest generation of the Echolodia lineup'
			/>
			<p>
				This year, we have a new color on this truck, and we call it Dirt Blue. It is a great color,
				and we think you'll love it. The electrical interface has been redesigned for simplicity and
				ease of use. More fuel, a fifth wheel adapter, a horn, better idling, larger buttons, and so
				much more.
			</p>
			<p>
				A new T9 engine is over 40% more powerful than last year's engine with RECO 1.3. The tow
				capacity has been greatly improved, and with a fifth-wheel adapter, Echolodia can tow much
				greater loads.
			</p>
			<CustomImage
				imagePath='/src/assets/images/stormworks/echolodia/eng.jpg'
				altText='The powerful new SentyTek T9 engine of Echolodia 2023'
			/>

			<div class='rounded-3xl bg-gray-300 dark:bg-gray-800 p-8 text-center'>
				<CustomImage
					imagePath='/src/assets/images/stormworks/echolodia-te/hero.jpg'
					altText='Echolodia TE, the more powerful and capable version of Echolodia, with a new T12 engine and a fifth wheel adapter'
				/>
				<h4 class='text-xl font-bold mb-2'>Maybe check out TE?</h4>
				<p class='text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300'>
					Echolodia TE is the more powerful, more capable version of Echolodia. With a new T12
					engine, a fifth wheel adapter, and more, it's the ultimate truck for those who need more.
				</p>
				<a
					href='/stormworks/echolodia-te'
					class='inline-block mt-4 px-4 py-2 bg-sky-500 hover:bg-sky-600 text-white font-medium rounded-full transition-colors'
					>Learn More</a
				>
			</div>

			<h3>Interior</h3>
			<p>
				SenCar 5 Lite now takes the place of where the old dashboard was. SenCar 5 is the greatest
				car operating system in Stormworks, and it's fantastic in the Echolodia. In this model,
				SenCar 5 doesn't convert the entire truck to digital, but enough to enhance the experience.
				New RBG lights allow a warmer entrance. The heater has been simplified into just a single
				button, and a map has been added to the rear for passengers to enjoy.
			</p>
			<CustomImage
				imagePath='/src/assets/images/stormworks/echolodia/int.jpg'
				altText='The interior of the Echolodia 2023, featuring the new SenCar 5 Lite dashboard'
			/>

			<h2>SenCar 5</h2>
			<p>
				SenCar 5 is the successor to the powerful car operating system, SenTOS Car 4. SenCar 5
				enhances your car with all new personalization features, a brand new UI, and more. SenCar 5
				features a brand new UI, made from scratch, with as little compromises as possible. SenCar 5
				is designed to take over nearly every element of a car. Built on top of the powerful SenOS
				architecture, it is easier than ever to control a car now.
			</p>
			<CustomImage
				imagePath='/src/assets/images/stormworks/echolodia/dash.jpg'
				altText='The SenCar 5 dashboard in Echolodia 2023, showing the new UI'
			/>
			<p>
				SenCar 5 features 7 themes to customize your experience with the car to the max. Custom
				currated colors match each theme perfectly, so that they dont contrast eachother. All of
				these settings can be changed from the microcontroller properties menu.
			</p>

			<h2>So much more</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>Horn</li>
				<li>Downshift protection</li>
				<li>Shows open doors on dashboard</li>
				<li>Enhanced trip stats</li>
				<li>Low fuel/battery alarms</li>
				<li>Enhanced clutch</li>
				<li>Developer support</li>
				<li>Open source</li>
				<li>More settings</li>
				<li>More "on-the-fly" settings</li>
			</ul>

			<ImageCarousel
				images={[
					{
						path: '/src/assets/images/stormworks/echolodia/bed.jpg',
						alt: 'Echolodia has a spacious bed for cargo and equipment'
					},
					{
						path: '/src/assets/images/stormworks/echolodia/tow.jpg',
						alt: 'Echolodia towing setup, showing the new fifth wheel adapter'
					}
				]}
			/>

			<p>
				<a
					href='https://github.com/SentyFunBall/SW-SenCar-5'
					target='_blank'
					rel='noreferrer'
					class='underline text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-400 dark:hover:text-blue-300'
					>SenCar 5 Source Code & Dev updates</a
				>
			</p>
			<p>
				<a
					href='https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-_KnjahEiBI'
					target='_blank'
					rel='noreferrer'
					class='underline text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-400 dark:hover:text-blue-300'
					>Watch the trailer on YouTube</a
				>
			</p>

			<h2 id='specs'>Specs</h2>
			<table>
				<tbody>
					<tr>
						<th>Engine</th>
						<td>9cyl supercharged 1x1</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<th>Transmission</th>
						<td>5 speed AutoManual</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<th>OS</th>
						<td>SenCar 5 with SiBTaT</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<th>ECU</th>
						<td>RECO 1.3</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<th>Top Speed</th>
						<td>105mph/170kph</td>
					</tr>
				</tbody>
			</table>

			<h2>Micros used</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>SenCar v5.0</li>
				<li>Custom SIBTaT Controller</li>
				<li>RECO v1.3</li>
			</ul>
		</article>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>

<script>
	import { animate } from 'motion'
	const showAnimations = localStorage.getItem('animations') === 'true'

	if (showAnimations) {
		animate(
			'.title',
			{ y: [80, 0], opacity: [0, 1] },
			{
				duration: 2.5,
				opacity: { duration: 3 },

				offset: [0, 0.55, 0.75]
			}
		)
	}
</script>
